@Node HIST "The History of this Door..."

  -=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-
                          History of this Door
  -=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-

    Version 1.2 (23rd April 1997)
    ~~~~~~~~~~~
   O - Now works with Multi-Node BBS's Thanks to NSA's Multitask Patcher.

    Version 1.1 (24th March 1997)
    ~~~~~~~~~~~
   O - Removed ShareWare Routines as PowerDOORS are now FreeWare.
   O - Updated Included ANSI File to Speed up Operation.

    Version 1.0 (2nd March 1997)
    ~~~~~~~~~~~
   O - Added Graph and Cycling Number Routines to improve Aesthetics
       of the Door.
   O - Added `BulletinDoor.Text' and `GuestDoor.Text' support as well
       as `MainDoor.Text' which has always been available.

    Version 0.9 (1st Februrary 1997) - Private Sub-Bass Version
    ~~~~~~~~~~~
   O - Added Configuration Support.
   O - Added Script/ANSI File

   @{" [0] " Link MAIN} Return to the Main Menu

@EndNode HIST

